The '''Goluud Corridor''' was a treacherous [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace route]] discovered by [[Jori Daragon|Jori]] and [[Gav Daragon]] that involved a jump past the unstable [[Red giant/Legends|red giant]] [[Primus Goluud/Legends|Primus Goluud]]. It was approved by the [[Hyperspace Navigator's Guild]], until ''[[Zeta Five]]'' passed to closely to the unstable star and exploded, discrediting the Daragons and forcing them to leave [[Cinnagar/Legends|Cinnagar]].

